The evidence with the title 'Floor speech on the economy - senator Bernie Sanders of Vermont ' says Nov 30, 2010  ... Last year , ExxonMobil made $19 billion in profit. Guess what. They paid zero in taxes . They got a $156 million refund from the IRS. I guess that is not good enough . We have to give the oil companies even more tax breaks. So i think that is where we are . We have to own up to it. There is a war going on. 
